Unit "1..*" -- "1..*" Trait
Unit "1" --> "1" Ability

Trait "1" -- "1..*" Trait_bonus

Ability "*" --> "1..*" Effect
Trait_bonus "*" --> "1..*" Effect

Object "*" --> "1..*" Effect

